[{"Code":"en","Title":"Overview","Slug":"identify-verification-overview","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"4cef62a1-2451-43fe-9e0a-ccc126e75bd6\">Our Identity Verification products can be used to verify your customers before you onboard them or process their transactions. With our verification API products you can:</p><ul data-block-id=\"7086cf55-2706-4ba1-8338-fc427f95fefa\"><li data-block-id=\"a38319e8-c17f-4f66-b3ce-3d7b9aa74592\"><p data-block-id=\"97a44730-fa66-47c3-9f63-6eba9d1fa0a3\">Verify your customer’s identity</p></li><li data-block-id=\"678d1db2-1245-47de-8713-88b44e9fd227\"><p data-block-id=\"08b11640-4192-4414-b2d7-4ed4adaabc4a\">Verify your customer’s bank accounts</p></li><li data-block-id=\"107605ef-4113-44f5-acf8-d5e063f9a16a\"><p data-block-id=\"7f543819-d41a-420d-9e82-0e4ac62770eb\">Check whether your customer is in a Sanctions watchlist</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"dfdb4b00-7414-4495-bd51-d8d7ad0415ee\">Verification products</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1094\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1094px;width:1094px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:191px;\"><col style=\"width:121px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"483c09d5-4ce2-487c-94da-d11c61fb5edd\">Product</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"218e5ed9-05a3-452d-94c4-1819cc9c718c\">Supported countries</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"25ce5285-fe35-4edd-a03c-b83f3e26faf2\">Function</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"34dc4e9f-c9da-4428-a42a-12cad56d5c44\">Common use cases</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"546f6b2b-f174-4d4c-85d1-747f4a76754c\">Bank Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"be82783e-a6af-4c86-b789-d87490a8dd6e\">Indonesia, Vietnam</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"949c645a-f196-4a81-8725-2ec368e94011\">To verify whether:</p><ul data-block-id=\"7a10f8ee-145e-406d-a8ed-16e818cd4b01\"><li data-block-id=\"6c80f65f-07ac-42e4-bb02-35f59c926103\"><p data-block-id=\"909fac5f-08ba-42c2-b748-e780357dbcfa\">A bank account number is valid</p></li><li data-block-id=\"b568460c-0980-4b3a-934a-4b8544aff974\"><p data-block-id=\"87a10a7f-85ca-4eba-baef-e6c717c4f4ee\">The account holder name matches the given name</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"b62c2fef-80f0-4645-90e8-8da8b84f039d\">Remittance businesses often need to verify their customers’ bank or E-Wallet accounts before sending funds.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"e06d53a6-ca3e-4c39-8683-0de1847267a8\">E-Wallet Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"73f3f01c-90a3-49c1-81d1-cf0d3e7a497f\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"4e5a01c1-428a-4d74-a7ce-052cd06725a0\">Checks whether an E-Wallet account exists for the given phone number</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"0207294e-601b-42b4-be7d-660cf690ddfe\">Individual Authentication</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"2692e1eb-455b-45ec-bdb8-2b997e1eca9a\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3ac3f27b-7a47-42c3-bde2-300085ae21c8\">Verifies and matches an individual’s ID number, full name and date of birth</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"2cf8aa28-8ead-435d-804a-e7516c76f0e8\">Various businesses need to ensure they are onboarding legitimate customers and prevent stolen identities.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"545fbe17-a8ba-43ee-a247-21a9bdfa14b1\">ID Card Verification</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"db42a6e2-b44a-4f89-8c6e-c03a35ac051d\">Philippines</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"82746b3c-10ca-4c97-94fe-1e9e2d710752\">Displays a pop-up for customers to complete a selfie and an ID card portrait</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"273ffd08-3ca1-4927-bb01-3ea027966dd8\">OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"a96dc81d-3a70-4366-8455-a8f0f77292a0\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"660ee1d5-c1e9-40b2-a52b-95ce5f6f0977\">Extracts text data from an ID card photo (KTP, NPWP)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"b588aabc-d588-4bfa-a0b5-956ae54413ee\">Eliminates data entry for customers that need to present their IDs.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"970ec85a-830b-45ac-8af6-c139d30dd9d5\">CFT Screening</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"ef21bfbb-618c-4574-b146-0733cb442521\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e51aefd4-af45-433b-945f-f72ff45f8a9e\">Matches a given name against one of Iluma’s supported sanctions watchlists</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"55816b15-93d0-4dfa-a152-b4417be24a64\">AML (Anti-money laundering) measures when onboarding customers.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"19aa48ae-71b8-47fb-991c-2cf87f6cb0f8\"><img data-block-id=\"00cca7d7-2bc3-40b4-9286-3a6437b59df8\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/iluma-logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"81\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:257px;height:81px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ca9ea2b5-c3fa-4418-8796-8f41cb617fbb\">Currently these API products are hosted under our Iluma brand. Refer to <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Iluma’s API Reference</a> for a full list of endpoints.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"31a8da07-570e-494d-af66-c0174fe9e5b8\">How to integrate with Iluma</h2><ol data-block-id=\"45aed5b5-afe5-4d03-bd11-eef97c82637e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f3338ad5-c52f-420e-8e91-847913f7e6fa\"><p data-block-id=\"18763304-a954-4b36-978d-46187b411530\">Send us a message to tell us you need an Iluma account. You will need to give us the following details</p><ol data-block-id=\"f7f098ab-e2ef-4246-8bc2-1c1b250d20c7\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ecd0b4a8-6be8-40b3-a98f-d58bb3b41c7a\"><p data-block-id=\"48df5b4e-8337-48e7-a82a-733f19dba1ff\">Basic business information (Business and PIC names, email, phone number, address)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d34b5ffd-288a-4971-8b08-6e91be4a86c2\"><p data-block-id=\"c3578e28-68d3-41b6-b86c-db8a74737812\">Which products you would like to use</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"4ba87e2e-64c3-48e8-8064-993c95c9a1cc\"><p data-block-id=\"38fc3708-df47-40e6-b8e1-8e4cafb9f7f6\">We will process the request and provide you the account details within 1-2 business days</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52124d79-7d5c-4b7c-a6cc-0f1104304ec1\"><p data-block-id=\"71d03ffe-2001-4410-ac68-3fc5db10aa59\">Use the given <code>token</code> to <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#get-api-key\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">get your API keys</a></p><ol data-block-id=\"503d9cb7-5694-4a1c-95f3-3bb3d3deab7f\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"147116f6-ab02-43dd-bfbe-3c2c5dd9bd8b\"><p data-block-id=\"bb3fe814-cc31-4a3a-bd5f-565bf836ad95\">This will return both a <code>live</code> and <code>development</code> key for testing purposes</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"11ebc024-3b71-461b-a4ae-951b0622e594\"><p data-block-id=\"e5a15052-6939-47e3-bccc-26a54899392d\">Complete and e-sign the agreement shared with you</p></li><li data-block-id=\"79c3a43c-50b2-4d7e-bee6-364581187159\"><p data-block-id=\"abc9f274-6d06-4f9e-a3d7-f4e1c05e0580\">Your account will be updated to Live status, and you can start verifying with real data</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"fffaec76-aa09-435c-8f72-f34297fa2ce5\">You can also follow the <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#integration-guide\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Iluma integration guide here</a></p><p data-block-id=\"e0e5284c-7542-4f09-99e9-c54003d6a64b\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Overview","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Overview","Slug":"overview-10","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-eos631-069\">Produk Verifikasi Identitas kami dapat digunakan untuk memverifikasi pelanggan Anda sebelum Anda menerima atau memproses transaksi mereka. Dengan produk API verifikasi kami, Anda dapat:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-gmvqf5-070\"><li data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-clq12q-071\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-t9oflb-072\">Memverifikasi identitas pelanggan Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-6hftct-073\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-0j0zes-074\">Memverifikasi rekening bank pelanggan Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-lgb71t-075\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-uix5di-076\">Memeriksa apakah pelanggan Anda ada dalam daftar pantauan sanksi</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"mcim94cv-q6z4yz-077\">Produk verifikasi</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1094\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1094px;width:1094px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:191px;\"><col style=\"width:121px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cw-esm2cd-078\">Produk</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cw-5dbbd4-079\">Negara yang didukung</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cw-g24o46-080\">Fungsi</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-y4wsnw-081\">Kasus penggunaan</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-v7qsa4-082\">Bank Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-y76jfb-083\">Indonesia, Vietnam</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-52znhn-084\">Untuk memverifikasi apakah:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-z0xedb-085\"><li data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-pcqjnm-086\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-x6m04k-087\">Nomor rekening bank valid</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-zot5db-088\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cx-d72j2z-089\">Nama pemegang akun cocok dengan nama yang diberikan</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cy-pmuiki-090\">Bisnis remitansi uang seringkali perlu memverifikasi rekening bank atau E-Wallet pelanggan mereka sebelum mengirim dana.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cy-vl7ihy-091\">E-Wallet Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cy-9yclmf-092\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cy-99f5jv-093\">Memeriksa apakah ada akun E-Wallet untuk nomor telepon yang diberikan</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cy-3miblc-094\">Autentikasi Individu</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cy-s0m68v-095\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-b5fzwz-096\">Memverifikasi dan mencocokkan nomor ID, nama lengkap, dan tanggal lahir individu</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-tw5tq8-097\">Berbagai bisnis perlu memastikan bahwa mereka melakukan orientasi pelanggan yang sah dan mencegah identitas yang dicuri.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-n39mjc-098\">Verifikasi KTP</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-pk03ci-099\">Filipina</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-1pr2ac-100\">Menampilkan pop-up bagi pelanggan untuk menyelesaikan selfie dan potret kartu identitas</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-a04utg-101\">OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94cz-fa8cpy-102\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d0-07mdz2-103\">Mengekstrak data teks dari foto KTP (KTP, NPWP)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d1-k7u5h7-104\">Menghilangkan entri data bagi pelanggan yang perlu menunjukkan ID mereka.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d1-0pjzv3-105\">Skrining CFT</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d1-gcxh95-106\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d1-uqg6v2-107\">Mencocokkan nama pemberian dengan salah satu daftar pantauan sanksi yang didukung Ilema</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d1-mrsrxo-108\">Langkah-langkah AML (Anti pencucian uang) saat orientasi pelanggan.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d1-rdbblv-109\"><img data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-wr8h8b-110\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/iluma-logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"81\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:257px;height:81px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-znomrl-111\">Saat ini produk API ini dihosting di bawah merek Iluma kami. Lihat <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">API Reference Iluma</a> untuk daftar lengkap titik akhir.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-z4evm3-112\">Cara integrasi dengan Iluma</h2><ol data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-40wun4-113\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-gfihjn-114\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-498176-115\">Kirimkan email kepada kami untuk memberi tahu kami bahwa Anda memerlukan akun Iluma. Anda harus memberi kami detail berikut</p><ol data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-gq2yvr-116\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-wlugr8-117\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-u9q44y-118\">Informasi bisnis dasar (Nama bisnis dan PIC, email, nomor telepon, alamat)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-uydppg-119\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-4jiyv5-120\">Produk mana yang ingin Anda gunakan</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-u9a5va-121\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d2-uy7aam-122\">Kami akan memproses permintaan dan memberi Anda detail akun dalam waktu 1-2 hari kerja</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-wuwbnh-123\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-4650hs-124\">Gunakan yang diberikan <code>token</code> untuk <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#get-api-key\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">mendapatkan API key Anda</a></p><ol data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-hqpn4q-125\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-tvig1t-126\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-j0iilx-127\">Ini akan mengembalikan key <code>live</code> dan <code>development</code> untuk tujuan pengujian</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-yovh1l-128\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-5q31ib-129\">Lengkapi dan tandatangani perjanjian yang dibagikan kepada Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-yd5c7h-130\"><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-a1ubmx-131\">Akun Anda akan diperbarui ke status Live, dan Anda dapat mulai memverifikasi dengan data nyata</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-rncbm3-132\">Anda juga dapat mengikuti <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#integration-guide\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">panduan integrasi Iluma di sini</a>.</p><p data-block-id=\"mcim94d3-v7oh6s-133\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Overview","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ภาพรวม","Slug":"overview-10","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"4cef62a1-2451-43fe-9e0a-ccc126e75bd6\">ผลิตภัณฑ์ Identity Verification ของเราสามารถใช้เพื่อยืนยันลูกค้าของคุณก่อนที่คุณจะเริ่มใช้งานหรือดำเนินการธุรกรรมของพวกเขา ด้วยผลิตภัณฑ์ API สำหรับการยืนยันของเรา คุณสามารถ:</p><ul data-block-id=\"7086cf55-2706-4ba1-8338-fc427f95fefa\"><li data-block-id=\"a38319e8-c17f-4f66-b3ce-3d7b9aa74592\"><p data-block-id=\"97a44730-fa66-47c3-9f63-6eba9d1fa0a3\">ยืนยันตัวตนของลูกค้าของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"678d1db2-1245-47de-8713-88b44e9fd227\"><p data-block-id=\"08b11640-4192-4414-b2d7-4ed4adaabc4a\">ยืนยันบัญชีธนาคารของลูกค้าของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"107605ef-4113-44f5-acf8-d5e063f9a16a\"><p data-block-id=\"7f543819-d41a-420d-9e82-0e4ac62770eb\">ตรวจสอบว่าลูกค้าของคุณอยู่ในรายชื่อเฝ้าระวังการคว่ำบาตร (Sanctions watchlist) หรือไม่</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"dfdb4b00-7414-4495-bd51-d8d7ad0415ee\">ผลิตภัณฑ์การยืนยัน (Verification products)</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1094\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1094px;width:1094px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:191px;\"><col style=\"width:121px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"483c09d5-4ce2-487c-94da-d11c61fb5edd\">ผลิตภัณฑ์ (Product)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"218e5ed9-05a3-452d-94c4-1819cc9c718c\">ประเทศที่รองรับ (Supported countries)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"25ce5285-fe35-4edd-a03c-b83f3e26faf2\">ฟังก์ชัน (Function)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"34dc4e9f-c9da-4428-a42a-12cad56d5c44\">กรณีการใช้งานทั่วไป (Common use cases)</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"546f6b2b-f174-4d4c-85d1-747f4a76754c\">Bank Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"be82783e-a6af-4c86-b789-d87490a8dd6e\">Indonesia, Vietnam</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"949c645a-f196-4a81-8725-2ec368e94011\">เพื่อยืนยันว่า:</p><ul data-block-id=\"7a10f8ee-145e-406d-a8ed-16e818cd4b01\"><li data-block-id=\"6c80f65f-07ac-42e4-bb02-35f59c926103\"><p data-block-id=\"909fac5f-08ba-42c2-b748-e780357dbcfa\">หมายเลขบัญชีธนาคารถูกต้อง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"b568460c-0980-4b3a-934a-4b8544aff974\"><p data-block-id=\"87a10a7f-85ca-4eba-baef-e6c717c4f4ee\">ชื่อเจ้าของบัญชีตรงกับชื่อที่ระบุ</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"b62c2fef-80f0-4645-90e8-8da8b84f039d\">ธุรกิจการโอนเงินมักจะต้องยืนยันบัญชีธนาคารหรือบัญชี E-Wallet ของลูกค้าก่อนที่จะส่งเงิน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"e06d53a6-ca3e-4c39-8683-0de1847267a8\">E-Wallet Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"73f3f01c-90a3-49c1-81d1-cf0d3e7a497f\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"4e5a01c1-428a-4d74-a7ce-052cd06725a0\">ตรวจสอบว่ามีบัญชี E-Wallet อยู่สำหรับหมายเลขโทรศัพท์ที่ระบุหรือไม่</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"0207294e-601b-42b4-be7d-660cf690ddfe\">Individual Authentication</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"2692e1eb-455b-45ec-bdb8-2b997e1eca9a\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3ac3f27b-7a47-42c3-bde2-300085ae21c8\">ยืนยันและจับคู่หมายเลข ID, ชื่อเต็ม และวันเกิดของบุคคล</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"2cf8aa28-8ead-435d-804a-e7516c76f0e8\">ธุรกิจต่างๆ จำเป็นต้องมั่นใจว่าพวกเขากำลังเริ่มใช้งานลูกค้าที่ถูกต้องตามกฎหมายและป้องกันการขโมยตัวตน</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"545fbe17-a8ba-43ee-a247-21a9bdfa14b1\">ID Card Verification</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"db42a6e2-b44a-4f89-8c6e-c03a35ac051d\">Philippines</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"82746b3c-10ca-4c97-94fe-1e9e2d710752\">แสดงป๊อปอัปให้ลูกค้าถ่ายเซลฟี่และรูปถ่ายบัตรประจำตัว</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"273ffd08-3ca1-4927-bb01-3ea027966dd8\">OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"a96dc81d-3a70-4366-8455-a8f0f77292a0\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"660ee1d5-c1e9-40b2-a52b-95ce5f6f0977\">ดึงข้อมูลข้อความจากรูปถ่ายบัตรประจำตัว (KTP, NPWP)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"b588aabc-d588-4bfa-a0b5-956ae54413ee\">ลดการป้อนข้อมูลสำหรับลูกค้าที่ต้องแสดงบัตรประจำตัว</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"970ec85a-830b-45ac-8af6-c139d30dd9d5\">CFT Screening</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"ef21bfbb-618c-4574-b146-0733cb442521\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e51aefd4-af45-433b-945f-f72ff45f8a9e\">จับคู่ชื่อที่ระบุกับรายชื่อเฝ้าระวังการคว่ำบาตรที่ Iluma รองรับ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"55816b15-93d0-4dfa-a152-b4417be24a64\">มาตรการ AML (การต่อต้านการฟอกเงิน) เมื่อเริ่มใช้งานลูกค้า</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"19aa48ae-71b8-47fb-991c-2cf87f6cb0f8\"><img data-block-id=\"00cca7d7-2bc3-40b4-9286-3a6437b59df8\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/iluma-logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"81\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:257px;height:81px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ca9ea2b5-c3fa-4418-8796-8f41cb617fbb\">ปัจจุบัน ผลิตภัณฑ์ API เหล่านี้โฮสต์ภายใต้แบรนด์ Iluma ของเรา โปรดดู <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Iluma’s API Reference</a> สำหรับรายการ endpoint ทั้งหมด</p><h2 data-block-id=\"31a8da07-570e-494d-af66-c0174fe9e5b8\">วิธีการเชื่อมต่อกับ Iluma (How to integrate with Iluma)</h2><ol data-block-id=\"45aed5b5-afe5-4d03-bd11-eef97c82637e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f3338ad5-c52f-420e-8e91-847913f7e6fa\"><p data-block-id=\"18763304-a954-4b36-978d-46187b411530\">ส่งข้อความถึงเราเพื่อแจ้งว่าคุณต้องการบัญชี Iluma คุณจะต้องให้รายละเอียดดังต่อไปนี้แก่เรา</p><ol data-block-id=\"f7f098ab-e2ef-4246-8bc2-1c1b250d20c7\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ecd0b4a8-6be8-40b3-a98f-d58bb3b41c7a\"><p data-block-id=\"48df5b4e-8337-48e7-a82a-733f19dba1ff\">ข้อมูลธุรกิจพื้นฐาน (ชื่อธุรกิจและชื่อผู้ติดต่อ (PIC), อีเมล, หมายเลขโทรศัพท์, ที่อยู่)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d34b5ffd-288a-4971-8b08-6e91be4a86c2\"><p data-block-id=\"c3578e28-68d3-41b6-b86c-db8a74737812\">ผลิตภัณฑ์ที่คุณต้องการใช้</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"4ba87e2e-64c3-48e8-8064-993c95c9a1cc\"><p data-block-id=\"38fc3708-df47-40e6-b8e1-8e4cafb9f7f6\">เราจะดำเนินการตามคำขอและให้รายละเอียดบัญชีแก่คุณภายใน 1-2 วันทำการ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52124d79-7d5c-4b7c-a6cc-0f1104304ec1\"><p data-block-id=\"71d03ffe-2001-4410-ac68-3fc5db10aa59\">ใช้ <code>token</code> ที่ได้รับเพื่อ <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#get-api-key\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">รับ API keys ของคุณ</a></p><ol data-block-id=\"503d9cb7-5694-4a1c-95f3-3bb3d3deab7f\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"147116f6-ab02-43dd-bfbe-3c2c5dd9bd8b\"><p data-block-id=\"bb3fe814-cc31-4a3a-bd5f-565bf836ad95\">สิ่งนี้จะส่งคืนทั้ง <code>live</code> และ <code>development</code> key สำหรับวัตถุประสงค์ในการทดสอบ</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"11ebc024-3b71-461b-a4ae-951b0622e594\"><p data-block-id=\"e5a15052-6939-47e3-bccc-26a54899392d\">กรอกและลงนามในข้อตกลงทางอิเล็กทรอนิกส์ (e-sign) ที่เราได้แบ่งปันกับคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"79c3a43c-50b2-4d7e-bee6-364581187159\"><p data-block-id=\"abc9f274-6d06-4f9e-a3d7-f4e1c05e0580\">บัญชีของคุณจะได้รับการอัปเดตเป็นสถานะ Live และคุณสามารถเริ่มการยืนยันด้วยข้อมูลจริงได้</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"fffaec76-aa09-435c-8f72-f34297fa2ce5\">คุณยังสามารถทำตาม <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#integration-guide\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">คู่มือการเชื่อมต่อ Iluma ได้ที่นี่</a></p><p data-block-id=\"e0e5284c-7542-4f09-99e9-c54003d6a64b\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ภาพรวม","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Generalidades","Slug":"identify-verification-overview","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"4cef62a1-2451-43fe-9e0a-ccc126e75bd6\">Nuestros productos de Verificación de Identidad pueden utilizarse para verificar a sus Clientes antes de incorporarlos o de procesar sus Transacciones. Con nuestros productos API de verificación, usted puede:</p><ul data-block-id=\"7086cf55-2706-4ba1-8338-fc427f95fefa\"><li data-block-id=\"a38319e8-c17f-4f66-b3ce-3d7b9aa74592\"><p data-block-id=\"97a44730-fa66-47c3-9f63-6eba9d1fa0a3\">Verificar la identidad de su Cliente</p></li><li data-block-id=\"678d1db2-1245-47de-8713-88b44e9fd227\"><p data-block-id=\"08b11640-4192-4414-b2d7-4ed4adaabc4a\">Verificar las Cuentas bancarias de su Cliente</p></li><li data-block-id=\"107605ef-4113-44f5-acf8-d5e063f9a16a\"><p data-block-id=\"7f543819-d41a-420d-9e82-0e4ac62770eb\">Verificar si su Cliente se encuentra en una lista de vigilancia de Sanciones</p></li></ul><h2 data-block-id=\"dfdb4b00-7414-4495-bd51-d8d7ad0415ee\">Productos de verificación</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"1094\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:1094px;width:1094px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:191px;\"><col style=\"width:121px;\"><col style=\"width:406px;\"><col style=\"width:376px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"483c09d5-4ce2-487c-94da-d11c61fb5edd\">Producto</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"218e5ed9-05a3-452d-94c4-1819cc9c718c\">Países admitidos</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"25ce5285-fe35-4edd-a03c-b83f3e26faf2\">Función</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"34dc4e9f-c9da-4428-a42a-12cad56d5c44\">Casos de uso comunes</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"546f6b2b-f174-4d4c-85d1-747f4a76754c\">Bank Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"be82783e-a6af-4c86-b789-d87490a8dd6e\">Indonesia, Vietnam</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"949c645a-f196-4a81-8725-2ec368e94011\">Para verificar si:</p><ul data-block-id=\"7a10f8ee-145e-406d-a8ed-16e818cd4b01\"><li data-block-id=\"6c80f65f-07ac-42e4-bb02-35f59c926103\"><p data-block-id=\"909fac5f-08ba-42c2-b748-e780357dbcfa\">Un número de Cuenta bancaria es válido</p></li><li data-block-id=\"b568460c-0980-4b3a-934a-4b8544aff974\"><p data-block-id=\"87a10a7f-85ca-4eba-baef-e6c717c4f4ee\">El Nombre del titular de la Cuenta coincide con el Nombre proporcionado</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"b62c2fef-80f0-4645-90e8-8da8b84f039d\">Las empresas de remesas a menudo necesitan verificar las Cuentas bancarias o de E-Wallet de sus Clientes antes de enviar fondos.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"e06d53a6-ca3e-4c39-8683-0de1847267a8\">E-Wallet Validator</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"73f3f01c-90a3-49c1-81d1-cf0d3e7a497f\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"4e5a01c1-428a-4d74-a7ce-052cd06725a0\">Verifica si existe una Cuenta de E-Wallet para el número de Teléfono proporcionado</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"0207294e-601b-42b4-be7d-660cf690ddfe\">Individual Authentication</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"2692e1eb-455b-45ec-bdb8-2b997e1eca9a\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"3ac3f27b-7a47-42c3-bde2-300085ae21c8\">Verifica y coteja el número de ID, el Nombre completo y la Fecha de nacimiento de un individuo</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"2\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"2cf8aa28-8ead-435d-804a-e7516c76f0e8\">Varias empresas necesitan asegurarse de que están incorporando Clientes legítimos y prevenir el robo de identidades.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"545fbe17-a8ba-43ee-a247-21a9bdfa14b1\">ID Card Verification</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"db42a6e2-b44a-4f89-8c6e-c03a35ac051d\">Philippines</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"82746b3c-10ca-4c97-94fe-1e9e2d710752\">Muestra una ventana emergente para que los Clientes completen una selfie y un retrato de su tarjeta de ID</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"273ffd08-3ca1-4927-bb01-3ea027966dd8\">OCR</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"a96dc81d-3a70-4366-8455-a8f0f77292a0\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"660ee1d5-c1e9-40b2-a52b-95ce5f6f0977\">Extrae datos de texto de una foto de tarjeta de ID (KTP, NPWP)</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"b588aabc-d588-4bfa-a0b5-956ae54413ee\">Elimina la entrada de datos para los Clientes que necesitan presentar sus ID.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"191\"><p data-block-id=\"970ec85a-830b-45ac-8af6-c139d30dd9d5\">CFT Screening</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"121\"><p data-block-id=\"ef21bfbb-618c-4574-b146-0733cb442521\">Indonesia</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"406\"><p data-block-id=\"e51aefd4-af45-433b-945f-f72ff45f8a9e\">Coteja un Nombre proporcionado con una de las listas de vigilancia de sanciones admitidas por Iluma</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"376\"><p data-block-id=\"55816b15-93d0-4dfa-a152-b4417be24a64\">Medidas AML (Anti-money laundering) al incorporar Clientes.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"19aa48ae-71b8-47fb-991c-2cf87f6cb0f8\"><img data-block-id=\"00cca7d7-2bc3-40b4-9286-3a6437b59df8\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/iluma-logo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"81\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:257px;height:81px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"ca9ea2b5-c3fa-4418-8796-8f41cb617fbb\">Actualmente, estos productos API están alojados bajo nuestra marca Iluma. Consulte la <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">Referencia API de Iluma</a> para obtener una lista completa de endpoints.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"31a8da07-570e-494d-af66-c0174fe9e5b8\">Cómo integrar con Iluma</h2><ol data-block-id=\"45aed5b5-afe5-4d03-bd11-eef97c82637e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"f3338ad5-c52f-420e-8e91-847913f7e6fa\"><p data-block-id=\"18763304-a954-4b36-978d-46187b411530\">Envíenos un Mensaje para informarnos que necesita una Cuenta de Iluma. Deberá proporcionarnos los siguientes detalles</p><ol data-block-id=\"f7f098ab-e2ef-4246-8bc2-1c1b250d20c7\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"ecd0b4a8-6be8-40b3-a98f-d58bb3b41c7a\"><p data-block-id=\"48df5b4e-8337-48e7-a82a-733f19dba1ff\">Información básica del Comercio (Nombres del Comercio y del PIC, Correo electrónico, número de Teléfono, Dirección)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"d34b5ffd-288a-4971-8b08-6e91be4a86c2\"><p data-block-id=\"c3578e28-68d3-41b6-b86c-db8a74737812\">Qué productos le gustaría utilizar</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"4ba87e2e-64c3-48e8-8064-993c95c9a1cc\"><p data-block-id=\"38fc3708-df47-40e6-b8e1-8e4cafb9f7f6\">Procesaremos la request y le proporcionaremos los detalles de la Cuenta en un plazo de 1 a 2 días hábiles</p></li><li data-block-id=\"52124d79-7d5c-4b7c-a6cc-0f1104304ec1\"><p data-block-id=\"71d03ffe-2001-4410-ac68-3fc5db10aa59\">Utilice el <code>token</code> proporcionado para <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#get-api-key\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">obtener sus API keys</a></p><ol data-block-id=\"503d9cb7-5694-4a1c-95f3-3bb3d3deab7f\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"147116f6-ab02-43dd-bfbe-3c2c5dd9bd8b\"><p data-block-id=\"bb3fe814-cc31-4a3a-bd5f-565bf836ad95\">Esto devolverá una key <code>live</code> y una key <code>development</code> para fines de prueba</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"11ebc024-3b71-461b-a4ae-951b0622e594\"><p data-block-id=\"e5a15052-6939-47e3-bccc-26a54899392d\">Complete y firme electrónicamente el acuerdo compartido con usted</p></li><li data-block-id=\"79c3a43c-50b2-4d7e-bee6-364581187159\"><p data-block-id=\"abc9f274-6d06-4f9e-a3d7-f4e1c05e0580\">Su Cuenta se actualizará al Estado Live y podrá comenzar a verificar con datos reales</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"fffaec76-aa09-435c-8f72-f34297fa2ce5\">También puede seguir la <a href=\"https://docs.iluma.ai/#integration-guide\" target=\"_blank\" translate=\"no\">guía de integración de Iluma aquí</a></p><p data-block-id=\"e0e5284c-7542-4f09-99e9-c54003d6a64b\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Generalidades","Description":null}]